Summary:
When user attempts to log in with false username or password, or without providing any information, he/she will not succeed, but no warning message will be displayed. It would be better if there is a message saying the log in failed.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on More button on the bottom of screen.
2. Click on Log In button.
3. Leave fields empty and press OK.
Result: Log In window is closed and user is not logged in.